Horrible. Very noisy. Cockroaches and rats are swarming around the estate, attracting python snakes in search for food. Do not recommemd

Beautiful, sprawling grounds nestled on top of a hill. Feels like Iâ€™m in a castle!

Taking a visit back here after all these years seems like a trip back to an idyllic time, when I came home each day to a peaceful town safely isolated from the busy world lying just beyond it's groomed shrubs and cream coloured walls. Very thankful indeed for the days I spent here during my early childhood!
